quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  42,52,"Ko wano non Min mbayayinir e maa…óa, ruuhu on [Alqur'aana] e yamiroore Amen. A anndaano ko woni deftere, maa goo≈ã…óinal; si ko woni, Min mba…óunde ndaygu, ngu Min peewwnirta on mo Min muuyani e jiyaa…ìe Amen …ìen. Pellet, ko a feewnoowo e laawol Pocciingol,"
  42,53,"laawol Allah, On jey…óo ko woni kammuuji e ka leydi. ganndee, ko ka Allah, fiyakuuji …óin nduttotoo."
  43,1,"Haa, miim."
  43,2,"Mi woo…óndirii defere …ìanngunde ndeen !"
  43,3,"Min ma…óii nde janngeteende [e …óemngal] aarabu, mbelajo'o, on kaqqilay."
  43,4,"Pellet, hende woni ka Amen gaa, ka yumma defte, toownde, √±e√±aande."
  43,5,"E Min ngacciray njippinangol on jantoore ndeen, …óuurngal on, fii on ngonii yim…ìe fantin…ìe?"
  43,6,"∆äuu…óii e Annabaa…ìe …ìe Min nuli e adinoo…ìe …ìeen."
  43,7,"Annabaajo araali e ma…ì…ìe, si wonaa …ìe njalkitay mo."
  43,8,"Min kalki ko …ìuri …ìe sa…ótude doole ! Toode mise adinoo…ìe …ìeen jawtiino."
  43,9,"Ko pellet, si a lamndike …ìe: "Ko hommbo tagi kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin?" ∆Åe mbi'ay: "Ko poolu…óo, ganndu…óo on tagi …óii"."
  43,10,"Oon mba…óiran…óo on leydi ndin weertaandi, O wa…óani on …óate e mayri, fii no …óoworon."